{"tid":2035392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：外交界大量關注聲明證外國勢力非常猖獗","createTime":"2020-05-26T01:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T02:05:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2e84dc13c6b2a5a23e3950f34296fdb99cb9e6ef","tid":2035392,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"人民日報海外版：立法打擊外部亂港勢力十分必要<br />\n26.05.2020 05:46<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》海外版評論員文章指，全國人大審議涉港草案的議程公布後，就受到美英等外國和外部勢力的「格外關注」，可見外部勢力「亂港成性」，赤裸裸干預香港事務、干預香港內政，成為他們習以為常、理所當然之事。這更加凸顯了制定港區國安法是刻不容緩，十分必要。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，在維護國家安全和核心利益問題上，中國沒有任何妥協的空間。立法懲治危害國家安全的罪行，懲治外部勢力的深度干預，幫助香港遠離「顏色革命」和激進分裂勢力攬炒的深淵，築牢國安根基，中國的決心不可低估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290350&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1290350%26csid%3D261_341&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=1aa9d1ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290350&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"650e80e7fa530f830838efd9480d0b381a464b19","tid":2035392,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"突發<br />\n支那係巴西都奶野<br />\n極大量巴西人祝蔡英文上任同時支持香港<br />\n急需twitter師打國際線<br />\n<br />\n【Twitter戰線火山爆發】 &quot;#VivaTaiwan&quot; : World Trending #1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035385</a>"},{"pid":"f763195c37ccf9789450cc3dcce96f48dfca9f38","tid":2035392,"uid":11454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:29:16.000Z","msg":"一邊叫外資唔好走， 一邊屌外國勢力<br />\n精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0ca0969cb11cfebbb5b63d822e2c6f19c0a58e","tid":2035392,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"得！下次天災你哋自己玩賓州啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" 